msgstr "Ограничения безопасности"

#: pgcrypto.xml:1267(para)
msgid ""
"All <filename>pgcrypto</filename> functions run inside the database server. "
"That means that all the data and passwords move between <filename>pgcrypto</"
"filename> and client applications in clear text. Thus you must:"
